<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="7Oct1935"><font color="red">7 October 1935</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): I wrote to Mr Desmond Flower of the <i>Sunday Times</i> informing him that Mr Joyce was willing for a page of his MS to be exhibited and that I would send one to him on loan as soon as I had the opportunity of going up to town. </div>
